Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.group.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class Group
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity class that modeling data base table Group. Contains queries for extraction the information from the table, columns and relation to the other tables. The purpose of the table is to saves information about different groups like name, head of the group, etc.
